text: :For a nearby similar named village, see Wissenkerke in Netherlands or Wissekerke Castle in Bazel. Wissekerke is a village in the Dutch province of Zeeland. It is located in the municipality of Goes Wissekerke was a separate municipality until 1816, when it was merged with 's-Heer Hendrikskinderen. ==References== Category:Populated places in Zeeland Category:Former municipalities of Zeeland Category:Goes
